{"id":"guide/i18n-common-overview","title":"Common Internationalization tasks","contents":"\n\n\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/i18n-common-overview.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"common-internationalization-tasks\" translation-result=\"on\">常見的國際化任務<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-overview#common-internationalization-tasks\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1><h1 translation-origin=\"off\">Common Internationalization tasks<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-overview#common-internationalization-tasks\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">使用以下 Angular 任務來國際化你的專案。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Use the following Angular tasks to internationalize your project.</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">使用內建管道以本地格式顯示日期、數字、百分比和貨幣。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Use built-in pipes to display dates, numbers, percentages, and currencies in a local format.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在元件範本中標記文字以進行翻譯。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Mark text in component templates for translation.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">標記出要翻譯的表示式的複數形式。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Mark plural forms of expressions for translation.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">標記替代文字進行翻譯。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Mark alternate text for translation.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在為國際受眾準備好專案之後，可以使用 <a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> 來本地化你的專案。完成以下任務以本地化你的專案。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">After you prepare your project for an international audience, use the <a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> to localize your project.\nComplete the following tasks to localize your project.</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">使用 CLI 將標記的文字提取到<em>源語言</em>檔案中。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Use the CLI to extract marked text to a <em>source language</em> file.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">為每種語言製作一份<em>源語言</em>檔案的副本，並將所有<em>翻譯</em>檔案傳送給翻譯人員或翻譯服務。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Make a copy of the <em>source language</em> file for each language, and send all of <em>translation</em> files to a translator or service.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在為一種或多種語言環境建構專案時，使用 CLI 合併已完成的翻譯檔案。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Use the CLI to merge the finished translation files when you build your project for one or more locales.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"alert is-helpful\">\n<p translation-result=\"on\">為所有目標語言環境建立一個強適應性的使用者介面，將不同語言的間距等差異考慮在內。有關更多詳細資訊，請參閱<a href=\"https://marketfinder.thinkwithgoogle.com/intl/en_us/guide/how-to-approach-i18n#overview\" title=\"Overview - How to approach internationalization | Market Finder | Think with Google\">如何進行國際化</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Create an adaptable user interface for all of your target locales that takes into consideration the differences in spacing for different languages.\nFor more details, see <a href=\"https://marketfinder.thinkwithgoogle.com/intl/en_us/guide/how-to-approach-i18n#overview\" title=\"Overview - How to approach internationalization | Market Finder | Think with Google\">How to approach internationalization</a>.</p>\n\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"prerequisites\" translation-result=\"on\">前提條件<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-overview#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Prerequisites<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-overview#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要準備翻譯專案，你應該對以下主題有基本的瞭解。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To prepare your project for translations, you should have a basic understanding of the following subjects.</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#template\" title=\"template - Glossary | Angular\">範本</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#template\" title=\"template - Glossary | Angular\">Templates</a></p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#component\" title=\"component - Glossary | Angular\">元件</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#component\" title=\"component - Glossary | Angular\">Components</a></p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> <a href=\"guide/glossary#command-line-interface-cli\" title=\"command-line interface (CLI) - Glossary | Angular\">命令列</a>，管理 Angular 開發週期的工具</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> <a href=\"guide/glossary#command-line-interface-cli\" title=\"command-line interface (CLI) - Glossary | Angular\">command-line</a> tool for managing the Angular development cycle</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/XML\" title=\"Extensible Markup Language (XML) | W3C\">XML</a> 用於翻譯檔案</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/XML\" title=\"Extensible Markup Language (XML) | W3C\">Extensible Markup Language (XML)</a> used for translation files</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"learn-about-common-angular-internationalization-tasks\" translation-result=\"on\">瞭解常見的 Angular 國際化任務<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-overview#learn-about-common-angular-internationalization-tasks\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Learn about common Angular internationalization tasks<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-overview#learn-about-common-angular-internationalization-tasks\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<div class=\"card-container\">\n    <a href=\"guide/i18n-common-add-package\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Add the localize package\">\n      <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">新增 localize 套件</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Add the localize package</section>\n      \n      <p translation-result=\"on\">學習如何往專案中新增 Angular 的 localize 套件</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Learn how to add the Angular Localize package to your project</p>\n      \n      <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">新增 localize 套件</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Add the localize package</p>\n      \n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/i18n-common-locale-id\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Refer to locales by ID\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">透過 ID 參考語言環境</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Refer to locales by ID</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">學習如何標識語言環境識別符號，並將其新增到專案</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Learn how to identify and specify a locale identifier for your project</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">透過 ID 參考語言環境</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Refer to locales by ID</p>\n    \n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Format data based on locale\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">基於語言環境格式化資料</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Format data based on locale</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">學習如何實現本地化資料管道，以及為專案改寫預設語言環境</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Learn how to implement localized data pipes and override the locale for your project</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">基於語言環境格式化資料</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Format data based on locale</p>\n    \n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/i18n-common-prepare\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Prepare component for translation\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">準備翻譯元件</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Prepare component for translation</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">學習如何指定要翻譯的源文字</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Learn how to specify source text for translation</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">為翻譯準備元件</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Prepare component for translation</p>\n    \n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/i18n-common-translation-files\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Work with translation files\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">使用翻譯檔案</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Work with translation files</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">學習如何檢查和處理翻譯檔案</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Learn how to review and process translation text</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">使用翻譯檔案</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Work with translation files</p>\n    \n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/i18n-common-merge\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Merge translations into the application\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">把翻譯結果合併回應用</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Merge translations into the application</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">學習如何合併翻譯結果，並建構翻譯完的應用</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Learn how to merge translations and build your translated application</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">把翻譯結果合併回應用</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Merge translations into the application</p>\n    \n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/i18n-common-deploy\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Deploy multiple locales\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">部署多個語言環境</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Deploy multiple locales</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">學習如何為應用部署多個語言環境</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Learn how to deploy multiple locales for your application</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">部署多個語言環境</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Deploy multiple locales</p>\n    \n  </a>\n</div>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最後複查時間：10/7/2021</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - guide/i18n-overview\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - cli\n - guide/glossary#command-line-interface-cli\n - guide/glossary#component\n - guide/glossary#template\n - guide/i18n-common-add-package\n - guide/i18n-common-deploy\n - guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale\n - guide/i18n-common-locale-id\n - guide/i18n-common-merge\n - guide/i18n-common-overview#common-internationalization-tasks\n - guide/i18n-common-overview#learn-about-common-angular-internationalization-tasks\n - guide/i18n-common-overview#prerequisites\n - guide/i18n-common-overview#瞭解常見的-angular-國際化任務\n - guide/i18n-common-overview#前提條件\n - guide/i18n-common-overview#常見的國際化任務\n - guide/i18n-common-prepare\n - guide/i18n-common-translation-files\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/i18n-common-overview.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n - https://marketfinder.thinkwithgoogle.com/intl/en_us/guide/how-to-approach-i18n#overview\n - https://www.w3.org/XML\n-->"}